					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&#8230;&#8230;&#8230; What? No.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">SPOILER</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">No&nbsp;spoiler</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>1782 was a self-aware reality warper even <em>in utero</em>. Mommy was slowly being driven mad by it and/or general living conditions, and either tried to abort the baby or suffered a miscarriage. Baby didn't like that and didn't want to let mommy go.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Unless somehow that's exactly what you meant.</p> 
				 	]]>
